channel.title: Extracurricular on Zaeem Ahmad
channel.description: Recent content in Extracurricular on Zaeem Ahmad

item.title: Datavvy Data Analysis
item.description: Dipping my toe in the world of data science with the help of senior data engineer and entrepreneur Sakibul Hassan. Many hours of troubleshooting with my buddy Mohammad Mahrus!

item.title: Nightblade
item.description: My friend and I won second place with our line-tracking robot at the ECE Summer Robotics Competition (hosted by UofT’s ECE Department). Everyone had loads of fun!

item.title: ECE Hardware Workshop
item.description: A hardware workshop hosted by Professor Hamid Shokrallah and UofT’s ECE department focused on introductory electronics and discrete analog circuits.

item.title: MedTray
item.description: My first ever hackathon, MakeUofT (happens to be Canada’s largest hardware hackathon), where two of my buddies and I developed a prototype for an automatic medicine dispenser for elderly people
